  "texts": [
    "Fig. 4f depicts the relationship between bandgap and Tg data extracted by the pipelines.",
    "GPT-3.5 demonstrated the ability to capture more data including numerous extreme property values, while Materi-alsBERT successfully captured values towards the center of the distribution.",
    "Additionally, both methods illustrate the scarcity of materials exhibiting high bandgaps and simultaneously high Tg values.",
    "Six data points with high bandgap or Tg values, as determined by the pipelines, are identified and numbered in Fig. 4f.",
    "The pipelines correctly extracted points 1, 2, and 3."
  ]
